  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, combine orange segments, red onion, and cilantro.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together lime juice, kombu cold extract, salt, black pepper, and coriander.",
    "Pour the lime juice mixture over the orange mixture and toss to coat.",
    "Gently fold in diced avocado.",
    "Cover the bowl with plastic wrap and refrigerate for at least 30 minutes to allow the flavors to meld.",
    "Just before serving, give the ceviche a good stir and adjust the seasoning if needed.",
    "Serve the ceviche chilled, garnished with additional cilantro if desired.",
    "Cover and refrigerate any leftovers for up to 24 hours."
  ],
